er-width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1px 1px 1px 5px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div><iframe class=\"bdi-example\" title=\"<bdi> を使用した左書きと右書きのあるテキストの場合\" id=\"frame_bdi-sample-3\" height=\"120\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/bdi/_sample_.bdi-sample-3.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>","titleAsText":"<bdi> を使用した左書きと右書きのあるテキストの場合"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"仕様書","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>仕様書</th>\n      <th>状態</th>\n      <th>備考</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/semantics.html#the-bdi-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"ja\">&lt;bdi&gt; の定義</small></a></td>\n      <td><span class=\"spec-living\">現行の標準</span></td>\n      <td></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/textlevel-semantics.html#the-bdi-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"ja\">&lt;bdi&gt; の定義</small></a></td>\n      <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">勧告</span></td>\n      <td></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"ブラウザーの互換性","isH3":false,"query":"html.elements.bdi","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/bdi/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"関連情報","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/International/articles/inline-bidi-markup/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Inline markup and bidirectional text in HTML</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/International/articles/inline-bidi-markup/uba-basics\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Unicode Bidirectional Algorithm basics</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Localization\" class=\"page-not-created\" t